<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وابن حجر في <span class="c1">" التهذيب "</span> <span class="c2">(٤/١٧٠)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
